place_info.title: DEL style Osaka Higashi Temma by Daiwa Roynet Hotel
place_info.address: 2 Chome-6-3 Higashitenma, Kita Ward, Osaka, 530-0044, Japan

reviews.snippet: 房間乾淨，床的硬度支撐性ok，枕頭高度略高但還行，可惜大行李無法完全攤開放地上，只能半開，還好只住一晚，不然有點不方便。早餐是在附近的咖啡店用餐，只能說普通。
reviews.translated_snippet: The room was clean, the bed was firm and supportive, and the pillows were a bit high but fine. Unfortunately, the large luggage couldn't be fully unfolded on the floor and had to be half-opened. Fortunately, it was only a one-night stay, otherwise it would have been a bit inconvenient. Breakfast was served at a nearby cafe and was just average.

images.title: DEL style Osaka Higashi Temma by Daiwa Roynet Hotel

response.snippet: 感谢您分享住宿体验。我们很高兴您对客房清洁度和床铺舒适度感到满意。关于行李寄存处和早餐选择的问题，我们将认真听取您的意见，并致力于改进服务。
response.translated_snippet: Thank you for sharing your stay. We're glad you were satisfied with the cleanliness of your room and the comfort of your bed. Regarding the luggage storage and breakfast options, we'll take your feedback seriously and work hard to improve our service.

place_info.title: AB Hotel Kani
place_info.address: 6 Chome-54-番 Hiromi, Kani, Gifu 509-0214, Japan

reviews.snippet: 房間沒煙味就贏附近另一間飯店了，雖然空間不大只有13m2，但我的29吋大行李可以完全攤開放在地上，且不會影響我在房間的移動。床的硬度支撐性ok，枕頭也不會太高。早餐好吃但空間略顯擁擠。
reviews.translated_snippet: The room didn't smell like smoke, which was better than another nearby hotel. Although the space was small at only 13 square meters, my 29-inch luggage could be spread out on the floor without hindering my mobility. The bed was firm and supportive, and the pillows weren't too high. The breakfast was delicious, but the space was a bit cramped.

place_info.title: 明輝輪胎行
place_info.address: 500, Taiwan, Changhua County, Changhua City, Section 2, Zhongshan Rd, 35號

reviews.snippet: 早上出門突然發現胎壓異常，7點多附近只有這家有開，發現是釘子插到輪胎，但店家只能外補沒有內補，且外補收費400元😳，唯一優點就是趕時間的話只能靠這間了，但萬一還有下次的話我應該會多請一小時的假去做內外補，畢竟都是跑高速為主，只有外補無法放心，安全第一啊。三顆星都是給阿姨的，要換胎還要顧孫真的太辛苦了😓
reviews.translated_snippet: When I went out in the morning, I suddenly found that the tire pressure was abnormal. At 7 o'clock, only this store was open nearby. I found that a nail was stuck in the tire, but the store could only repair it externally, not internally, and the external repair cost 400 yuan😳. The only advantage is that if you are in a hurry, you can only rely on this store. But if there is a next time, I should take an extra hour off to do internal and external repairs. After all, I mainly drive on the highway, and I can't be assured of only external repairs. Safety first. Three stars are for the aunt, it is really too hard to change tires and take care of grandchildren😓

place_info.title: Brayy 茶食空間 彰化店－茶餐廳｜麵食｜麵店
place_info.address: 500, Taiwan, Changhua County, Changhua City, Tianxiang Rd, 39號

reviews.snippet: 點了麻醬拌麵、功夫麵、蛋煎麻香麵線、高麗菜、香酥雞、銀絲捲，原本都很好，直到最後上的蛋煎麻香麵線完全無鹹味扣了一顆星，可惜了
reviews.translated_snippet: I ordered sesame noodles, Kung Fu noodles, fried sesame noodles, cabbage, crispy chicken, and silver rolls. They were all good until the fried sesame noodles at the end had no saltiness at all, so I deducted one star. What a pity.

place_info.title: Marine Science Gallery, NMMST
place_info.address: 5樓 National Museum of Marine Science and Technology, No. 367號, Beining Rd, Zhongzheng District, Keelung City, Taiwan 202

reviews.snippet: 兒子光是主題館就半天玩不完了，兒童館也還沒玩到，下次可以考慮排整天
reviews.translated_snippet: My son spent half a day playing in the theme park and he still hasn't finished playing in the children's park. Next time, I might consider making a full day.

place_info.title: 清境英格曼鄉村花園民宿
place_info.address: 546, Taiwan, Nantou County, Ren’ai Township, Renhe Rd, 227號

reviews.snippet: 中部連日大雨擔心山區土石流風險詢問是否可以改期，老闆娘覺得很安全不給改，但我可不想為了幾千塊的普通住宿賭命，因為那些被土石流沖走的人當時應該也不覺得自己會有那麼危險或倒霉
reviews.translated_snippet: There have been heavy rains in central Taiwan for several days, and I was worried about the risk of landslides in the mountainous areas. I asked if I could reschedule my stay. The hostess said it was safe and refused. However, I didn't want to gamble my life for a few thousand dollars of ordinary accommodation. Those who were swept away by the landslides probably didn't think they were in such danger or unlucky at the time.

place_info.title: 京江小棧 New 料理餐廳
place_info.address: 500, Taiwan, Changhua County, Changhua City, Section 2, Zhongzheng Rd, 777號

reviews.snippet: 雖然五星評論有10元炸蝦可能衝高了一些分數，但餐點、服務、環境都真的很不錯，我覺得即使沒有刻意用五星衝高評論，分數應該也不會太低，唯一缺點大概就是無味的香濃巧克力，個人認為如果有成本考量其實可以把自助吧移除，無損我再訪用餐的意願
reviews.translated_snippet: Although the 10 yuan fried shrimp may have raised the score a bit, the food, service and environment are all really good. I think even if I didn't deliberately use five stars to raise the review, the score should not be too low. The only drawback is probably the tasteless rich chocolate. Personally, I think if there is a cost consideration, the self-service bar can actually be removed, which will not affect my willingness to visit again.

details.noise_level: Loud, but you can still talk

response.snippet:
非常感謝您給的評論，給每位師傅與服務生滿滿的鼓勵，歡迎下次可以再與您相遇。
廖先生/小姐 您提到的香濃巧克力，我們已做好處理了，因為用量較大，原物料的容器也較小，所以沒有了（我們已把原物料補上了）才會讓您喝到無味，不好意思🙇🏻‍♀️🙇🏻
response.translated_snippet:
Thank you very much for your comment, which gives full encouragement to every chef and waiter. Welcome to meet you again next time.
Mr./Ms. Liao We have already processed the rich chocolate you mentioned. Because the amount is large and the container of the original material is small, we have run out of it (we have replenished the original material) so you will find it tasteless. Sorry🙇🏻‍♀️🙇🏻

reviews.translated_snippet: Super comfortable hotel. Although the space is small as usual in Japanese hotels, this one makes good use of the space. The TV can be projected on the phone, there is steak for breakfast, and you can buy snacks and beer at night. Sitting in the massage chair and watching the night view is great~

reviews.translated_snippet: Nice hotel, the bed is supportive and not too soft, the room & bathroom are spacious and not too small, the breakfast is delicious, the TV can project YouTube, the only drawback is that the air conditioner blows directly at the bed

place_info.title: 可可娜咖啡🌴最後點餐5PM
place_info.address: 95491, Taiwan, Taitung County, Beinan Township, 杉原22號

reviews.snippet: 趕在下午五點前到，吃個點心喝杯飲料，看看海景還不錯，但要下去踏浪建議早點到，因需另外購票（非可可娜經營）且也只到六點
reviews.translated_snippet: Get there before 5pm, have a snack and drink, and enjoy the sea view. It's nice, but if you want to go down to the waves, it's recommended to arrive earlier because you need to buy a separate ticket (not operated by Cocona) and it's only until 6pm.

place_info.title: Lan Bai Shi B&B
place_info.address: No. 19號, Fenglong Rd, Guanshan Township, Taitung County, Taiwan 956

reviews.snippet: 環境清幽，但有點太清幽了，蟲蟲有點多，床偏軟個人喜歡硬的(腰受過傷)，排除以上都很好，早餐也好吃，喜歡大自然跟軟床的人應該會很愛
reviews.translated_snippet: The environment is quiet, but a little too quiet. There are a lot of bugs. The bed is soft. I like a hard one (I have a back injury). Excluding the above, it is good. The breakfast is also delicious. People who like nature and soft beds should love it.

place_info.title: Luye Highland
place_info.address: No. 46號, Gaotai Rd, Luye Township, Taitung County, Taiwan 955

reviews.snippet: 差點因為颱風看不到熱氣球，還好最後還是看到了
reviews.translated_snippet: I almost couldn't see the hot air balloon because of the typhoon, but fortunately I still saw it in the end

place_info.title: 娜路彎大酒店
place_info.address: 950, Taiwan, Taitung County, Taitung City, Lianhang Rd, 66號

reviews.snippet: 台東行遇到颱風，改行程在下雨最多的週日入住，雖然小貴，但我可是出來玩的，館內設施用好用滿，床的支撐性很好，早餐不錯吃，停車位有限建議早點來停
reviews.translated_snippet: I encountered a typhoon during my trip to Taitung, so I changed my itinerary to stay on Sunday when it rained the most. Although it was a little expensive, I came here to have fun. The facilities in the hotel were well used, the bed was very supportive, the breakfast was good, and the parking spaces were limited. It is recommended to park early.

place_info.title: 猛爸爸合菜‧快炒

reviews.snippet: 床的支撐性不錯不會太軟，環境清幽乾淨，早餐美而美，唯一美中不足是冷氣會一直吹到頭，需把頭躺在床尾才比較好一點，但瑕不掩瑜，有機會會再訪
reviews.translated_snippet: The bed is supportive and not too soft. The environment is quiet and clean. The breakfast is delicious. The only drawback is that the air conditioner blows all the way to your head. You need to lie at the end of the bed to feel better. However, the disadvantages are not enough to cover the advantages. I will visit again if I have the chance.

reviews.translated_snippet: The itinerary was changed temporarily on a rainy day. Free tea and snacks, Champion Tea blind test game, factory tour, the boss's introduction was humorous, and they also sold red bean cakes that were delicious and not too sweet.

place_info.title: WPAPA Teppanyaki Brunch
place_info.address: 1樓No. 16號, Lane 923, Tucheng Rd, Dali District, Taichung City, Taiwan 412

reviews.snippet: 好吃，生意非常好，但難停車、有點小貴、只收現金、無發票、上菜要等比較久，且有一突發狀況，不知為何店家的鐵皮天花板塞了衛生紙，也許是下雨漏水，但衛生紙後來剛好掉到我頭上再掉到桌上，告知店家後，雖有詢問是否有掉到食材上，也確實沒有，但沒掉到食材上就不用有什麼表示嗎？我想這沒有絕對對錯，也許是店家忙沒想太多，但以我個人來說再綜合以上其他缺點，應該是不會再訪了
reviews.translated_snippet: It tastes good and has very good business, but parking is difficult, it's a little expensive, they only accept cash, there are no invoices, you have to wait a long time for the dishes to be served, and there was an unexpected situation. I don't know why the store's iron ceiling was stuffed with toilet paper. Maybe it was raining and leaking, but the toilet paper happened to fall on my head and then on the table. After I informed the store, although I asked if it fell on the ingredients, it indeed didn't. But if it didn't fall on the ingredients, did they need to say anything? I think there is no right or wrong in this. Maybe the store owner was busy and didn't think too much about it. But for me personally, considering the other shortcomings mentioned above, I probably won't visit again.

place_info.title: NU PASTA 彰化中正店（最後點餐20:30）
place_info.address: 500, Taiwan, Changhua County, Changhua City, Section 2, Zhongzheng Rd, 680-5號

reviews.snippet: 其實吃很多次了，是好吃的，雖然最近活動越搞越多，還有line會員卡，但店員常常忘記要給活動的優惠，上次是忘記給折價卷，這次是忘記送薯條，然後最近兩次都沒有刷到會員卡，好的服務應該是要主動詢問客人有沒有會員，而不是結完帳就不能集點了。(更新：評論完沒多久就來問我會員說要幫我補登XD，等收到點數再來更新分數)
reviews.translated_snippet: In fact, I have eaten there many times and it is delicious. Although there are more and more events recently and there are line membership cards, the store clerk often forgets to give discounts for the events. Last time, he forgot to give discount coupons, this time he forgot to give out French fries, and the last two times I did not get the membership card. Good service should be to proactively ask customers if they are members, rather than not being able to collect points after settling the bill. (Update: Not long after I finished the comment, I was asked by members who wanted to help me re-register XD. I will update the score after receiving the points)

response.snippet:
您好  非常抱歉未能給您滿意的服務
在員工訓練的部分我們會一直持續加強
會員的部份我們每個月都會推出好友優惠，優惠券就可以來店消費時兌換優惠喔！
當然補點數的部分結帳後還是可以補點數的！
謝謝您的回饋🙏
response.translated_snippet:
Hello, I'm very sorry that I couldn't provide you with satisfactory service.
We will continue to strengthen employee training
For members, we launch friend discounts every month, and the coupons can be redeemed for discounts when you come to the store to make purchases!
Of course, you can still make up points after checkout!
Thank you for your feedback🙏

place_info.title: Park Plaza Faridabad
place_info.address: Sector 21C, Faridabad, Haryana 121002, India

reviews.snippet: 房間老舊，床單有污漬，廁所和浴室多處生鏽，洗手台會漏水，毛巾居然有一條是濕的，其他條毛巾看起來也不是很乾淨，沒附礦泉水，只有重複使用的玻璃瓶水，為了環保是很好，但在印度，礦泉水以外的冷飲我是不敢喝的，隔音也不好，不能說無法住人，但我不會想再來住，Google map寫是四星飯店，反差感極大。
reviews.translated_snippet: The room is old, the sheets are stained, the toilet and bathroom are rusty in many places, the sink leaks, one of the towels is wet, and the others don't look very clean either. There is no mineral water, only reusable glass bottles of water, which is good for environmental protection, but in India, I dare not drink cold drinks other than mineral water. The soundproofing is not good either. It can't be said that it is uninhabitable, but I would not want to stay here again. Google map says it is a four-star hotel, which is a huge contrast.

response.snippet: Thanks for sharing your feedback. We know that we can do better than this. Please be assured that we have taken your advice seriously & we are working on improving our services. Will you give us another chance?

この度は美浜殿内へご来店いただき、また温かい口コミをありがとうございます！席の手配がお役に立てたとのことで、嬉しく思っております。
ゴーヤの揚げ物や自分で作るすき焼きを気に入っていただけたこと、大変光栄です！どちらも多くのお客様にご好評いただいているメニューです。

ありがとうございました！

Dear Liao Xiaohei
Thank you for visiting Mihama Tonouchi and for your kind review! We are glad to hear that our seating arrangements were helpful.

Representative Katsuya Ikeda

place_info.address: 500, Taiwan, Changhua County, Changhua City, Lunmei Rd, 238號

reviews.snippet:
12/24這次點了薯餅蛋餅、蘿蔔糕煎蛋、奶茶、菇菇濃湯，都不錯而且這次有附醬包了👍，強烈建議用line訂餐，不然生意太好現場會等較久。

12/18豬肉漢堡蛋吐司肉滿厚的，不錯。
粉漿原味蛋餅少了醬油膏，不知道是太忙忘了加還是本來就設定不加，有點可惜。
豆漿不錯喝。
雖然無法內用，但這是離家最近的早餐店，希望繼續加油，還會再光顧的。
reviews.translated_snippet:
On December 24th, I ordered a hash brown omelet, a carrot cake omelet, milk tea, and mushroom soup. They were all delicious, and this time they came with a sauce packet. 👍 I highly recommend ordering via Line, otherwise the wait can be long at the counter due to the high volume.

On December 18th, I ordered a pork burger and egg toast. The meat was quite thick and delicious.
The plain batter omelet was missing soy sauce paste. I don't know if they forgot to add it because they were busy, or if it's not set in the menu. It's a shame.
The soy milk was delicious.
Although you can't eat in, this is the closest breakfast place to my home. I hope it keeps up the good work and I'll definitely be back.

response.snippet:
謝謝你給的回饋～～目前試營運中～
蛋餅都沒有➕醬料，我們有另外附醬料的服務，可能太忙沒有詢問您🙏🏻
有你的鼓勵～我們會堅持下去的🧡
response.translated_snippet:
Thank you for your feedback～～Currently in trial operation～
The omelettes don't have any sauce. We have a separate sauce service. Maybe I was too busy to ask you. 🙏🏻
With your encouragement, we will persevere.
